    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "BXV1I",
      "x": 18238,
      "y": 840,
      "name": "DIAG F — Read me: the craft rules",
      "clip": true,
      "width": 1280,
      "height": 720,
      "fill": "#26201B",
      "layout": "none",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "I45z4",
          "x": 80,
          "y": 56,
          "fill": "#E0A183",
          "content": "READ ME",
          "fontFamily": "Archivo",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "700",
          "letterSpacing": 2.4
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "xnNe9",
          "x": 80,
          "y": 86,
          "fill": "#F2ECE0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 1080,
          "content": "What the research changed, and the rules these five follow.",
          "lineHeight": 1.2,
          "fontFamily": "Fraunces",
          "fontSize": 38,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "bF0mw",
          "x": 80,
          "y": 200,
          "fill": "#F2ECE0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 500,
          "content": "Headline the conclusion, not the topic",
          "lineHeight": 1.25,
          "fontFamily": "Fraunces",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "i1RBE",
          "x": 80,
          "y": 252,
          "fill": "#B7ADA0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 490,
          "content": "Every title above is an argument you could disagree with. 'Our model' is not.",
          "lineHeight": 1.5,
          "fontFamily": "Archivo",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "BKe7C",
          "x": 640,
          "y": 200,
          "fill": "#F2ECE0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 500,
          "content": "Label directly. Never a legend",
          "lineHeight": 1.25,
          "fontFamily": "Fraunces",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "Go31e",
          "x": 640,
          "y": 252,
          "fill": "#B7ADA0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 490,
          "content": "A legend makes the eye do a lookup loop on every glance.",
          "lineHeight": 1.5,
          "fontFamily": "Archivo",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "NH5Oq",
          "x": 80,
          "y": 350,
          "fill": "#F2ECE0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 500,
          "content": "Five to seven objects, then split",
          "lineHeight": 1.25,
          "fontFamily": "Fraunces",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "RCn1z",
          "x": 80,
          "y": 402,
          "fill": "#B7ADA0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 490,
          "content": "Past that, people stop reading and start nodding.",
          "lineHeight": 1.5,
          "fontFamily": "Archivo",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "MzcIl",
          "x": 640,
          "y": 350,
          "fill": "#F2ECE0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 500,
          "content": "One arrow, one meaning",
          "lineHeight": 1.25,
          "fontFamily": "Fraunces",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "tOjGz",
          "x": 640,
          "y": 402,
          "fill": "#B7ADA0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 490,
          "content": "Material, money and influence must never share a stroke style.",
          "lineHeight": 1.5,
          "fontFamily": "Archivo",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "RT6Ox",
          "x": 80,
          "y": 500,
          "fill": "#F2ECE0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 500,
          "content": "A sentence beats a weak schematic",
          "lineHeight": 1.25,
          "fontFamily": "Fraunces",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "C8Wwe7",
          "x": 80,
          "y": 552,
          "fill": "#B7ADA0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 490,
          "content": "Under three relationships, write the sentence instead.",
          "lineHeight": 1.5,
          "fontFamily": "Archivo",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "hOQ60",
          "x": 640,
          "y": 500,
          "fill": "#F2ECE0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 500,
          "content": "Say 'not yet' inside the diagram",
          "lineHeight": 1.25,
          "fontFamily": "Fraunces",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "J6Ejq",
          "x": 640,
          "y": 552,
          "fill": "#B7ADA0",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 490,
          "content": "Faint gates, not a footnote. Honesty has to be visible at a glance.",
          "lineHeight": 1.5,
          "fontFamily": "Archivo",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "cIFPR",
          "x": 80,
          "y": 660,
          "fill": "#8A7F72",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 1120,
          "content": "Dropped after research: the stacked-area taper (the crossover disappears inside the stack) and the plain ring of arrows (decoration, not evidence). Sources: Berinato, Good Charts · Ellen MacArthur circular diagram convention · GIIN blended finance. Deck-specific sources are thin; most of this is reasoned from information-design literature.",
          "lineHeight": 1.5,
          "fontFamily": "Archivo",
          "fontSize": 12,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
